<div class="container">
<h1 class="mb-2">Welcome to the Support Ticket System</h1>

<p>Need assistance? You're in the right place! Our dedicated Support Ticket System is designed to offer you quick and effective help. Whether you're encountering a technical issue, need help with course content, or have administrative inquiries, just submit a ticket, and our support team will be on it promptly.
</p>
<p>
    How It Works:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Submit a Ticket: Describe your issue or question, providing as much detail as possible.</li>
    <li>Track Progress: Once submitted, you can track the progress of your ticket through updates and notifications.</li>
    <li>Resolution: Our team will work diligently to resolve your query and provide you with a detailed response.</li>
</ul>
<p>
    Start by clicking the button below to submit your first ticket. We're here to help ensure your experience is smooth and successful!
</p>

{{#cansubmittickets}}
    <input type="button" class="btn btn-primary p-2" value="Submit a Ticket" onclick="location.href='{{config.wwwroot}}/local/tickets/submit.php'" />
{{/cansubmittickets}}
<div class="mt-2">
    {{#ticketscount}}
        <input type="button" class="btn btn-secondary p-2" value="{{#str}}view_my_tickets, local_tickets{{/str}}" onclick="location.href='{{config.wwwroot}}/local/tickets/mytickets.php'" />
    {{/ticketscount}}
    <span class="mx-1">{{#str}}you_have_num_tickets, local_tickets, {{ticketscount}}{{/str}}</span>
</div>
{{#canmanagetickets}}
    <div class="my-4">
    <p>You Can Manage Tickets Since You're an admin</p>
    <input type="button" class="btn btn-warning p-2" value="{{#str}}manage_tickets, local_tickets{{/str}}" onclick="location.href='{{config.wwwroot}}/local/tickets/manage.php'" />
    </div>
{{/canmanagetickets}}
<hr>
</div>